ygData.messageBody:
Greetings one and all! I am a wandering merchant of sorts on the
Bertoxxulous server. I can get just about anything (including those rarer
spells and yes.... even combine, fine steel and well balanced weapons!) If
interested in buying a particular item or spell, (and you're on this server)
then please email me with your request and I will get back to you about it!
I charge fair prices to locate and deliver your item!
